<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9MWVQSNTMS7G" data-linktype="external">openEuler 22.09</a></li>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9P9RSPJDKX9G" data-linktype="external">openEuler 22.03</a></li>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9NWB78L1MPS2" data-linktype="external">openEuler 20.03</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>SUSE:
<ul>
<li>openSUSE:
<ul>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9MSSK2ZXXN11" data-linktype="external">openSUSE Tumbleweed</a></li>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9NJGLDP5G04B" data-linktype="external">openSUSE Leap 15.6</a></li>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9NJGLDP5G04B" data-linktype="external">openSUSE Leap 15.5</a></li>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9NJFZK00FGKV" data-linktype="external">openSUSE-Leap-15-1</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>SUSE Linux:
<ul>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9N738KZGNB91" data-linktype="external">SUSE Linux Enterprise 15 SP6</a></li>
<li><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9N648JDGXK2D" data-linktype="external">SUSE Linux Enterprise 15 SP5</a></li>
